reviewText:
I'm not a huge fan of combat games against other humans, I prefer the team work type against the living dead (...and trying not to be 'left for dead') ...but when I'm in a MP Combat mood, Minimum is brilliant. No need to even pay for in-game stuff, just play it and earn it within the game.

